text: Utvängstorp Church () is a church building in Mullsjö Municipality in Sweden. It is located circa two Scandinavian miles south of Tidaholm and two Scandinavian miles north of Mullsjö. It belongs to the Mullsjö-Sandhem Parish of the Church of Sweden. The church is dated back to the later 12th century. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:12th-century buildings and structures
